careers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20only%20possibility%20of%20Kohli%20or%20Pujara%20playing%20against%20Pakistan%20would%20be%20a%20potential%20World%20Test%20Championship%20(WTC)%20final%2C%20which%20would%20take%20place%20in%20a%20neutral%20venue.%20With%20Pakistan%20out%20of%20the%20race%20in%20the%202023-25%20cycle%2C%20such%20a%20scenario%20could%20only%20take%20place%20from%20the%20next%20cycle%20onwards.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20means%20that%20any%20India-Pakistan%20Test%20encounter%20is%20highly%20unlikely%20until%20at%20least%202027.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20and%20Pakistan%20will%20next%20square%20off%20in%20the%20Champions%20Trophy%202025%20at%20a%20neutral%20venue%2C%20despite%20Pakistan%20being%20the%20tournament's%20original%20hosts.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734877920000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2F3c5cevd_r-ashwin-afp_625x300_19_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffirst-time-in-147-years-ravichandran-ashwin-sets-unique-pakistan-record-after-retirement-7307877%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Ravichandran%20Ashwin's%20sudden%20retirement%20has%20made%20him%20the%20first%20player%20in%20cricket%20history%20to%20achieve%20something%20rather%20unique.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Ffirst-time-in-147-years-ravichandran-ashwin-sets-unique-pakistan-record-after-retirement-7307877%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Is%20Safe%20Car%20Enough%3F%20Volvo%20Crash%20That%20Killed%20CEO%2C%20Family%20Sparks%20Big%20Question%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20chilling%20crash%20of%20a%20Volvo%20SUV%20near%20Bengaluru%20yesterday%2C%20which%20claimed%20six%20lives%2C%20has%20sparked%20a%20conversation%20on%20how%20safe%20cars%20may%20not%20make%20a%20difference%20unless%20our%20roads%20are%20made%20safer.%20The%20Volvo%20XC90%2C%20considered%20the%20gold%20standard%20in%20car%20safety%2C%20was%20crushed%20by%20a%20container%20truck%20that%20jumped%20the%20divider%20on%20the%20Nelmangala-Tumkuru%20highway.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20victims%20have%20been%20identified%20as%20Chandram%20Yegapagol%20(48)%2C%20his%20wife%20Gourabai%20(42)%2C%20his%20son%20Gyan%20(16)%2C%20daughter%20Deeksha%20(12)%20sister-in-law%20Vijayalakshmi%20(36)%20and%20Vijayalakshmi's%20daughter%20Arya%20(6).%20Chandram%20Yegapagol%20was%20the%20managing%20director%20and%20CEO%20of%20IAST%20Software%20Solutions%2C%20a%20Bengaluru-based%20automotive%20solutions%20firm%2C%20and%20had%20reportedly%20bought%20the%20SUV%20just%20two%20months%20back.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20reports%2C%20the%20family%20was%20going%20to%20Sangli%20in%20neighbouring%20Maharashtra%20to%20meet%20Chandram's%20father.%20Police%20have%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fcity%2Fbengaluru%2Fbengaluru-it-firm-ceo-5-kin-killed-as-container-truck-falls-on-suv%2Farticleshow%2F116554082.cms%5C%22%3EThe%20Times%20of%20India%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20he%20was%20driving%20safely%20and%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20at%20fault%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EArif%2C%20the%20driver%20of%20the%20container%20truck%2C%20who%20suffered%20injuries%20in%20the%20accident%2C%20has%20told%20the%20media%20that%20the%20heavy%20vehicle%20jumped%20the%20divider%20while%20trying%20to%20save%20a%20car%20that%20stopped%20suddenly%20on%20the%20highway.%20%26quot%3BA%20car%20in%20front%20of%20me%20hit%20the%20brakes%20suddenly.%20When%20I%20hit%20the%20brakes%2C%20the%20truck%20kept%20going%20forward.%20To%20save%20the%20car%2C%20I%20swerved%20to%20the%20right%20and%20the%20truck%20jumped%20the%20divider%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20The%20truck%20then%20hit%20the%20milk%20truck%20before%20crushing%20the%20Volvo%20behind%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20driver%20said%20he%20was%20not%20aware%20of%20the%20fact%20that%20six%20people%20were%20killed%20in%20the%20accident.%20He%20said%20the%20truck%20was%20transporting%20aluminum.%20It%20must%20be%20pointed%20out%20that%20it%20is%20always%20difficult%20for%20loaded%20heavy%20vehicles%20to%20stop%20instantly%20because%20of%20their%20weight.%20This%20makes%20panic%20braking%20risky.%20The%20driver%2C%20Arif%2C%20has%20been%20booked%20for%20rash%20driving%20and%20death%20by%20negligence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accident%20has%20sparked%20a%20conversation%20on%20social%20media%2C%20with%20users%20pointing%20out%20that%20the%20safest%20of%20cars%20cannot%20save%20lives%20unless%20others%20on%20the%20road%20are%20driving%20safely.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriveSmart%2C%20a%20handle%20promoting%20safe%20driving%2C%20shared%20shocking%20pictures%20from%20the%20accident%20site.%20%26quot%3BThis%20pic%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20being%20safer%20on%20the%20road%20is%20not%20achieved%20by%20a%20safer%20car%20alone.%20Safe%20Roads%20%2B%20Safe%20Driver%20%2B%20Safe%20Car%3A%20All%20three%20are%20essential%20for%20safety.%20All%20the%20passengers%20in%20this%20Volvo%20lost%20lives%20in%20this%20car%20which%20supposedly%20went%20through%20all%20types%20of%20testing%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThis%20pic%20is%20a%20reminder%20that%20being%20safer%20on%20the%20road%20is%20not%20achieved%20by%20a%20safer%20car%20alone.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnSafe%20Roads%20%2B%20Safe%20Driver%20%2B%20Safe%20Car%20--%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20three%20are%20essential%20for%20safety.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnAll%20the%20passengers%20in%20this%20Volvo%20lost%20lives%20in%20this%20car%20which%20supposedly%20went%20through%20all%20types%20of%20testing.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F7p52rs2btF%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F7p52rs2btF%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20DriveSmart%F0%9F%9B%A1%EF%B8%8F%20(%40DriveSmart_IN)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FDriveSmart_IN%2Fstatus%2F187041979