r%20Kohli%2C%20Gavaskar%20feels%20the%20batter%20continues%20to%20try%20the%20cover%20drive%20as%20he%20has%20scored%20thousands%20of%20runs%20while%20attempting%20that%20shot.%20Gavaskar%20wants%20Kohli%20to%20dig%20into%20the%20archives%20and%20watch%20his%20own%20videos%20where%20he%20couldn't%20stop%20scoring%20tons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BLook%2C%20he's%20scored%20thousands%20of%20runs%20through%20that%20extra-cover%20drive%2C%26quot%3B%20Gavaskar%20told%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noindex%2Cnofollow%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Fcricket%2Fvirat-kohli-and-rohit-sharma-should-watch-videos-where-they-scored-centuries-after-centuries-sunil-gavaskar-to-ht-101734772164383.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fa%3E.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20something%20that%20is%20probably%20the%20best%20shot%20in%20the%20world%20today%2C%20the%20Virat%20Kohli%20extra-cover%20drive.%20Not%20so%20much%20the%20cover-drive%2C%20but%20the%20one%20that%20goes%20between%20mid-off%20and%20extra-cover.%20That's%20a%20wonderful%20shot%20to%20see.%20That's%20a%20full-face-of-the-bat%20shot.%20And%20because%20he%20gets%20so%20many%20runs%20from%20that%20shot%2C%20he's%20tempted%20to%20go%20for%20that%20because%20that's%20a%20very%20productive%20shot%20for%20him.%20Maybe%20that%20is%20the%20reason%20why%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20play%20over%20there%20and%20gets%20out.%20If%20you%20see%2C%20it's%20not%20that%20he%20has%20opened%20the%20face%20of%20the%20bat.%20It's%20not%20that%20he%20is%20looking%20to%20play%20to%20the%20covers.%20If%20that%20was%20happening%2C%20then%20you%20could%20say%2C%20hey%2C%20don't%20play%20towards%20cover.%20But%20it's%20a%20shot%20that%20has%20got%20him%20thousands%20of%20runs.%20Only%20this%20time%2C%20maybe%20the%20late%20movement%20is%20getting%20him%20out.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20asked%20what%20Kohli%20could%20do%20on%20the%20field%20to%20prevent%20himself%20from%20getting%20out%20in%20the%20same%20