n%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20as%20electric%20wires%20were%20being%20replaced.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20was%20no%20electricity%20in%20the%20area%20since%20evening.%20Due%20to%20this%20lack%20of%20air%20and%20being%20troubled%20by%20mosquitoes%2C%20my%20children%20lit%20the%20mosquito%20repellent%20sticks%20between%20two%20bricks%20and%20kept%20them%20under%20the%20bed%20they%20slept%20on.%20They%20were%20sleeping%20with%20a%20blanket%20on...there%20were%20also%20some%20clothes%20on%20the%20bed%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20neighbours%20helped%20them%20break%20into%20the%20room.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOur%20neighbours%20filled%20water%20in%20buckets%20and%20tried%20to%20extinguish%20the%20fire%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20victims'%20father%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20bodies%20of%20the%20victims%20have%20been%20sent%20for%20postmortem%20which%20will%20determine%20whether%20they%20died%20due%20to%20burns%20or%20smoke%20inhalation.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1734858720000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-12%2Fc8c9muo_mosqi_625x300_22_December_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fmosquito-repellent-sticks-ignite-fire-at-home-in-up-2-dead-7307040%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Two%20people%20died%20in%20a%20fire%20ignited%20due%20to%20mosquito%20repellent%20sticks%20at%20their%20home%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Ghaziabad%20on%20Saturday%20night.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fghaziabad-news%2Fmosquito-repellent-sticks-ignite-fire-at-home-in-up-2-dead-7307040%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Judge%20Tells%20Story%20Of%202%20Lawyers%2C%20One%20Became%20President%2C%20Other%20Chief%20Justice%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20rare%20display%20of%20emotion%20in%20public%2C%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%20Justice%20BV%20Nagarathna%20fought%20back%20tears%20while%20remembering%20her%20parents%20and%20her%20mother's%20lifelong%20support%20for%20her%20father%2C%20former%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India%20ES%20Venkataramiah.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%2C%20who%20is%20in%20line%20to%20be%20the%20country's%20first%20women%20chief%20justice%2C%20was%20addressing%20a%20gathering%20at%20the%20National%20Law%20School%20of%20India%20University%20in%20Bengaluru.%20The%20prestigious%20law%20school%20is%20hosting%20a%20lecture%20to%20mark%20the%20birth%20centenary%20of%20Chief%20Justice%20Venkataramiah%2C%20who%20taught%20there%20following%20his%20retirement.%20Justice%20PS%20Narasimha%2C%20also%20a%20Supreme%20Court%20judge%2C%20addressed%20the%20memorial%20lecture%20at%20the%20law%20school.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAddressing%20the%20event%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20said%20she%20considers%20it%20her%20good%20fortune%20that%20she%20found%20life's%20important%20lessons%20in%20her%20father's%20multifaceted%20personality.%20%26quot%3BI%20have%20always%20remained%20a%20student%20of%20law%20under%20his%20guidance.%20I%20have%20observed%20in%20him%20a%20strength%20of%20personality%2C%20which%20has%20only%20fortified%20my%20personal%20belief%20that%20fighting%20a%20good%20cause%20is%20most%20rewarding%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20said%20that%20her%20father's%20love%20for%20literature%20and%20Indian%20culture%20and%20his%20thirst%20for%20knowledge%20exposed%20her%20to%20varied%20subjects.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKnown%20for%20her%20sharp%20observations%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20fought%20back%20tears%20while%20remembering%20her%20mother's%20support%20to%20her%20father.%20%26quot%3BMy%20mother%2C%20Smt%20Padma%20was%20quick%20to%20appreciate%20what%20my%20father's%20true%20calling%20was.%20And%20left%20no%20stone%20unturned%20in%20supporting%20and%20enabling%20him%20to%20realise%20his%20dreams.%20importantly%2C%20she%20knew%20what%20it%20took%20to%20remain%20a%20conscientious%20and%20hard-working%20judge%20and%20always%20support%20him.%20She%20was%20known%20for%20her%20pragmatism%20and%20her%20patience%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said%20before%20inviting%20her%20top%20court%20colleague%20to%20deliver%20the%20lecture.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJustice%20Nagarathna%20could%20be%20seen%20wiping%20her%20eyes%20after%20she%20resumed%20her%20seat%20on%20the%20stage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20her%20address%2C%20Justice%20Nagarathna%20also%20recounted%20her%20father's%20words%20when%20he%20was%20elevated%20as%20a%20judge.%20%26quot%3BA%20judge%20is%20always%20on%20trial%20and%20I%20hope%20to%20be%20acquitted%20honourably%20at%20the%20end%20of%20my%20tenure.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20also%20narrated%20an%20interesting%20anecdote%20about%20two%20lawyers%20meeting%20on%20the%20train%20--%20one%20would%20go%20on%20to%20become%20the%20President%2C%20the%20other%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIn%20December%201946%2C%20the%20All%20India%20Lawyers'%20conference%20was%20held%20in%20Nagpur.%20Since%20there%20was%20no%20direct%20train%20between%20Bangalore%20and%20Nagpur%2C%20one%20had%20to%20go%20to%20Madras%20i.e.%20Chennai%20to%20take%20the%20Grand%20Trunk%20Express.%20In%20the%20railway%20compartment%2C%20there%20were%20a%20few%20lawyers%20travelling%20from%20Bangalore%20as%20well%20as%20Madras%20and%20everybody%20became%20friendly%20owing%20to%20shared%20interests%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BForty-three%20years%20later%2C%20in%20June%201989%2C%20two%20gentlemen%20from%20the%20railway%20compartment%20met%20at%20the%20Ashoka%20Hall%20of%20Rashtrapati%20Bhavan%2C%20one%20as%20the%20president%20of%20India%2C%20Shri%20R%20Venkataraman%20who%20was%20to%20swear%20in%20the%20other%2C%20Justice%20ES%20Venkataramaiah%20as%20the%20Chief%20Justice%20of%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20of%20India.%20When%20my%20father%20mentioned%20this%20to%20President%20R%20Venkataraman%20after%20the%20oath%20ceremony%